headline: Wall Street Analysts Have a Consensus Hold Recommendation on Brown & Brown, Inc. (BRO)
summary: Brown & Brown, Inc. (NYSE:BRO) is among the 11 Most Oversold S&P 500 Stocks Heading into 2026. On December 4, Citi analyst Matthew Heimermann maintained the firm’s Buy rating on the stock with a target price of $104, a reaffirmation of an earlier update on October 30.
